situation of the situation of Ms <b>Shammima Ali</b>, Coordinator of the Fiji Women&#8217;s Crisis Center, 
Ms <b>Edwina Kotoisuva</b>, Deputy Coordinator of the Fiji Women&#8217;s Crisis Center, Ms <b>Tevita 
Seruilumi</b>, Legal Officer of the Fiji Women&#8217;s Crisis Center, Ms <b>Noelene Nabulivou</b>, 
Coordinator of Women's Action for Change, Ms <b>Unaisi Dobui</b>, Ms <b>Tara Chetty</b>, Ms <b>Susan 
Naidu</b>, Ms <b>Michelle Reddy</b>, Ms <b>Neihmah Khan</b>, Ms <b>Claire Slatter,</b> Ms <b>Shirley Tagi</b> and Ms 
<b>Marlene Datta</b>, all members of the Fiji Women&#8217;s Rights Movement. According to the 
information received: 
 
