2248. According to the information received, on 14 August 2008 in the early morning hours, a 
brick was thrown at the window of Mr Dmitrievsky&#8217;s first-floor apartment. As a result the 
window was broken. At the same time, the front door to the apartment and the fa&#231;ade of the </p>

