on the question of torture and the Special Rapporteur on the promotion and protection of the 
right to freedom of opinion and expression, sent an urgent appeal <b>Karam Ibrahim Yousef</b>. Mr. 
Karam Ibrahim Yousef is a writer and human rights defender active in defence of the human 
