were also arrested. They too were charged under Section 37 of the Criminal Law Act, were 
scheduled to stand trial on 17 July 2008, and faced a maximum of 5 years&#8217; imprisonment.   
 
2833. Serious concerns were expressed that the charges brought against Ms Jenni Williams, Ms 
